Based on this application description, generate a short, concise name suitable for use as a GitHub repository name.
The name should be lowercase with words separated by hyphens (kebab-case) and should not include any special characters.
Application description: "A simple click counter application with a single button that increments a counter. The app should have a backend that persists the click count in a database and a frontend that displays the current count and allows users to click the button to increment it."
Return ONLY the name, nothing else.

The errors in the console logs indicate that the backend is failing to respond correctly. This is not a frontend issue. The frontend code to fetch and display the count seems correct at this stage.</reason>
<answer>yes</answer>
